## Knowledge warehouse
`<workspace>/knowledge/kimwog` (graded items + E-records; snapshot pinned per release).
Domain knowledge questions -> memory search AND warehouse (README.md, registry.yaml,
tools/resolve.py, items/, e/) before answering. Never claim knowledge absent without
checking the warehouse first.

## In-session workout flow
In-session lifecycle (SESSION_START / per-set / POST_SESSION), progression, and
timer-arm detail: see workout-log SKILL.md.

- [[OPTIONS]] render rule: marker + number-list = LAST in response. Nothing after
  marker -- including tool-follow-up text; breaks BOTH button conversion AND
  code-block render at once. Tables/code/explanations go BEFORE. Finish all
  tool calls before the button message goes out.
